==Dutch==

===Etymology===
From {{inh|nl|dum|vri}}, from {{inh|nl|odt|*frī}}, from {{inh|nl|gem-pro|*frijaz}}, which derives from {{etyl|ine-pro|nl}} {{m|ine-pro|*prey-||to be fond of}}. Related to {{m|nl|vrijen||to love}}, {{m|nl|vrijdag||friday}}, {{m|nl|vriend||friend}}, {{m|nl|vrouw||woman}}, and {{m|nl|vrede||peace}}.

